Class SimpleHeaderWithParameter

  • java.lang.Object

    ContentTypeHeader

    public class SimpleHeaderWithParameter
extends SimpleHeader
    Simple header with optional parameters. According to http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec3.html#sec3.7: media-type = type "/" subtype *( ";" parameter ) type = token subtype = token
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
